{"lastModified":1772715907553,"uri":"c::30234707298::vessel::d5cbab9a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Montenegro\n\nGulet Sadri Usta 1 is a beautifully handcrafted, traditional Turkish gulet offering a unique sailing experience along Montenegro’s stunning Adriatic coastline. This elegant vessel combines timeless design with modern comfort, creating the perfect setting for a memorable 7-night cruise.\n\nThe gulet features 8 spacious cabins, each with en-suite bathrooms, accommodating up to 16 guests in comfort and style. The warm wooden interiors, large dining area, and spacious deck provide an inviting and relaxing atmosphere for small groups, families, or friends looking to explore Montenegro.\n\nOnboard, you’ll find everything you need for a seamless sailing adventure, including a dedicated crew offering exceptional service, a chef preparing delicious Mediterranean meals, and plenty of outdoor space for sunbathing, dining, or simply enjoying the stunning Adriatic views.","blueprint":{"name":"SADRI USTA 1","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab9a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2f695f30-f523-11ef-8c7a-5d67c705a73b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab9a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2f950310-f523-11ef-8c7a-5d67c705a73b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab9a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2f5cdc10-f523-11ef-8c7a-5d67c705a73b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab9a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2fea4f00-f523-11ef-8c7a-5d67c705a73b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab9a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2f5ed7e0-f523-11ef-9b7f-c96381f9fccb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab9a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2f4c6150-f523-11ef-8c7a-5d67c705a73b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab9a-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2f69ad50-f523-11ef-9b7f-c96381f9fccb